# UI Rules

Follow the visual direction in:

- reference-dashboard-v1.png
- crm-ui-blueprint.md
- crm-backlog.md

## Layout

Use a premium SaaS CRM style:

- dark navy left sidebar
- bright white / light gray content area
- purple accent color
- rounded cards
- soft shadows
- clean Turkish labels
- compact but readable tables

## Sidebar

Sidebar must include a large logo area at the top.

Main sidebar items:

- Gosterge Paneli
- Hizli Islem
- Onaylar
- WhatsApp
- Cariler
- Urun / Stok
- Arsiv
- Raporlar
- Ayarlar

Do not use expanding archive submenus in the sidebar.

Archive category buttons must appear inside the Archive page content area, not inside the sidebar.

## Dashboard

AI Assistant right column appears only on the dashboard homepage.

The AI Assistant top area must look like a small video-capable screen with:

- play button
- progress bar
- control icons
- video frame styling

It should not look like an image upload box.

## Tables

List pages should show compact rows.

Target desktop density:

- at least 20 visible rows where possible
- clear columns
- row click opens detail modal

## Modals

Detail modal should include:

- record title
- customer / document information
- line items when relevant
- totals when relevant
- bottom action buttons

Typical modal actions:

- Duzenle
- Sil
- Kaydet
- Gonder
- Onayla
- Reddet
